---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const html = `<style>
    body { background: var(--innovia-navy); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); }

    .site-header {
      background: rgba(15,36,71,0.94);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
    }
    .site-header nav > a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    .site-header nav > a:hover, .site-header nav > a.active { color: #fff; }
    .site-header .btn-navy { background: #fff; color: var(--innovia-navy); }
    .site-header .btn-navy:hover { background: var(--innovia-green); color: var(--innovia-navy); }

    /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
    .page-hero {
      padding: 56px 0 64px;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .page-hero::after {
      content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 92% 8%, rgba(149,208,49,0.14) 0%, transparent 38%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 4% 96%, rgba(42,74,120,0.5) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .page-hero .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .page-hero .crumb {
      display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }
    .page-hero .crumb a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .page-hero .crumb .right {
      margin-left: auto;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    }
    .page-hero .crumb .right .dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--innovia-green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(149,208,49,0.7);
    }
    .page-hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 900;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 96px);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.034em;
      color: #fff; margin: 0;
      text-wrap: balance;
    }
    .page-hero h1 em { color: var(--innovia-green); font-style: normal; }
    .page-hero h1 .light {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-weight: 300; font-style: italic;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      font-size: 0.48em;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .page-hero .below {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-top: 36px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    }
    .page-hero .below p {
      font-size: clamp(17px, 1.3vw, 19px);
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      max-width: 56ch;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .page-hero .below .filters {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;
    }
    .page-hero .below .filter-label {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .page-hero .below .filter-row {
      display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .page-hero .below .filter-row .pill {
      padding: 7px 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
      font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      transition: all .15s; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .page-hero .below .filter-row .pill:hover { border-color: var(--innovia-green); color: #fff; }
    .page-hero .below .filter-row .pill.active {
      background: var(--innovia-green); color: var(--innovia-navy);
      border-color: var(--innovia-green); font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ---------- Audit banner ---------- */
    .audit-banner {
      padding: 0 0 24px;
    }
    .audit-banner .frame {
      padding: 18px 22px;
      background: rgba(149,208,49,0.08);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--innovia-green);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr auto;
      gap: 18px; align-items: center;
    }
    .audit-banner .icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: var(--innovia-green);
    }
    .audit-banner .text {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    }
    .audit-banner .text strong {
      display: block;
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--innovia-green);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .audit-banner a {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--innovia-green);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
      white-space: nowrap;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    }

    /* ---------- Resource grid ---------- */
    .resource-grid {
      padding: 24px 0 96px;
    }
    .resource-grid .row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    /* Featured tall card */
    .res-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      padding: 28px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .res-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--innovia-green);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 56px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .res-card .top {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .res-card .cat {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--innovia-green);
      letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      background: rgba(149,208,49,0.16);
    }
    .res-card .status {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 9px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .res-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: -0.014em;
      line-height: 1.18;
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 22ch;
      text-wrap: balance;
    }
    .res-card p {
      font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 52ch;
    }
    .res-card .foot {
      margin-top: auto;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }
    .res-card .foot .arrow { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); transition: color .15s, transform .15s; }
    .res-card:hover .foot .arrow { color: var(--innovia-green); transform: translateX(2px); }

    /* Grid spans */
    .res-card.feature {
      grid-column: span 6;
      grid-row: span 2;
      padding: 36px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(160deg, var(--innovia-navy-soft) 0%, var(--innovia-navy) 70%),
        var(--innovia-navy);
    }
    .res-card.feature h3 { font-size: clamp(28px, 3vw, 40px); max-width: 18ch; }
    .res-card.feature p { font-size: 15px; max-width: 44ch; }
    .res-card.wide  { grid-column: span 6; }
    .res-card.third { grid-column: span 4; }
    .res-card.half  { grid-column: span 6; }

    /* Green CTA card */
    .res-card.cta {
      background: var(--innovia-green);
      color: var(--innovia-navy);
      grid-column: span 6;
    }
    .res-card.cta h3, .res-card.cta p, .res-card.cta .foot { color: var(--innovia-navy); }
    .res-card.cta .cat { background: rgba(24,51,94,0.18); color: var(--innovia-navy); }
    .res-card.cta .foot { border-top-color: rgba(24,51,94,0.3); }
    .res-card.cta:hover { border-color: var(--innovia-navy); }
    .res-card.cta:hover .foot .arrow { color: var(--innovia-navy); }

    /* ---------- Asks (what we want to recreate) ---------- */
    .asks {
      padding: 96px 0 0;
      background: #FBFAF6;
      color: var(--fg-2);
    }
    .asks .container { padding-bottom: 96px; }
    .asks .head {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
      gap: 64px; align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }
    .asks .head h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--innovia-navy);
      font-size: clamp(36px, 4.4vw, 60px);
      letter-spacing: -0.024em;
      line-height: 1.04;
      max-width: 14ch;
      margin: 14px 0 0;
    }
    .asks .head p {
      font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.62;
      color: var(--fg-2);
      max-width: 56ch;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .asks .ask-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }
    .asks .ask {
      padding: 32px 28px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .asks .ask:last-child { border-right: 0; }
    .asks .ask .ix {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--innovia-green-deep);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .asks .ask h4 {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 19px;
      color: var(--innovia-navy);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .asks .ask p {
      font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--fg-2);
      margin: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .page-hero .below { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
      .resource-grid .row { grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr); }
      .res-card.feature, .res-card.cta { grid-column: span 6; grid-row: span 1; }
      .res-card.wide, .res-card.half { grid-column: span 6; }
      .res-card.third { grid-column: span 3; }
      .asks .head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
      .asks .ask-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .asks .ask { border-right: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); }
      .asks .ask:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .resource-grid .row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .res-card.feature, .res-card.wide, .res-card.half, .res-card.third, .res-card.cta { grid-column: span 1; }
      .audit-banner .frame { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    }
  </style>


  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="crumb">
        <a href="/">Innovia</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/find-a-management-company/">For Boards</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span style="color:#fff;">Resources &amp; Guides</span>
      </div>
      <h1>
        Resources for <em>HOA &amp; condo boards.</em>
        <span class="light">cooperatively authored. plainly written.</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="below">
        <p>The cooperatively-authored library for boards: how to evaluate a management company, what to look for in a reserve study, how Innovia members run an annual checkup, and the operating practices the cooperative shares across <span>80+</span>&nbsp;member companies.</p>
        <div class="filters">
          <div class="filter-label">Filter by topic</div>
          <div class="filter-row">
            <span class="pill active">All topics</span>
            <span class="pill">Choosing a manager</span>
            <span class="pill">Financials &amp; reserves</span>
            <span class="pill">Governance</span>
            <span class="pill">Vendor RFPs</span>
            <span class="pill">Practice</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RESOURCE GRID -->
  <section class="resource-grid">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">

        <a class="res-card feature" href="/solutions/switching-hoa-management/">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Choosing a manager</span>
            <span class="status">ACRI Community Realty</span>
          </div>
          <h3>How to choose the right community management company.</h3>
          <p>A board-facing guide from ACRI Community Realty &mdash; what to ask, what to compare, and the questions most boards forget before signing with a management company.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>10-min read &middot; Mar 2025</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card half" href="/board-education/hoa-reserve-study/">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Financials</span>
            <span class="status">Wise Property Solutions</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Twelve performance measures for an HOA annual checkup.</h3>
          <p>A working checklist for boards reviewing their management company&rsquo;s year. Originally published by Wise Property Solutions.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>7-min read &middot; Aug 2025</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card half" href="#">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Practice</span>
            <span class="status">CPE Property Management</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Clear communication and proactive planning.</h3>
          <p>How a member company brings the same operating practice to every community on its portfolio &mdash; even the difficult ones.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>6-min read &middot; Jul 2025</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card third" href="#">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Leadership</span>
            <span class="status">Great North Property Management</span>
          </div>
          <h3>What leadership looks like, inside an independent CAM company.</h3>
          <p>A profile of Great North Property Management &mdash; reframed for boards weighing how a manager&rsquo;s internal culture shows up on the ground.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>8-min read</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card third" href="#">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Excellence</span>
            <span class="status">Association Management Group</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Putting customer satisfaction first.</h3>
          <p>How Association Management Group structures internal scorecards around the boards they serve. Practical, copyable.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>5-min read</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card third" href="#">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Innovation</span>
            <span class="status">Silvercreek Association Management</span>
          </div>
          <h3>AI in HOA management: what works, what to be careful with.</h3>
          <p>A working-practitioner&rsquo;s view of where AI is genuinely useful in association management &mdash; and where it isn&rsquo;t yet.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>9-min read</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card cta" href="/find-a-management-company/#request">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">For boards</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Need management, not a guide?</h3>
          <p>If you&rsquo;re actively looking for a management company, skip the reading. Tell us about your community and we&rsquo;ll route the inquiry to the Innovia-backed member best positioned to serve you.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>~3 min &middot; no call lists</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card half" href="#">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Community</span>
            <span class="status">Condominium Financial Management</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Giving back: meaningful community impact through HOA management.</h3>
          <p>How Condominium Financial Management structures its philanthropic and community-engagement work &mdash; and how boards can support similar practices in their own portfolios.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>6-min read</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="res-card half" href="#">
          <div class="top">
            <span class="cat">Recognition</span>
            <span class="status">Nova Association Management</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Honoring excellence and innovation: a core-value award program.</h3>
          <p>Nova&rsquo;s internal recognition program &mdash; how the practice shapes the experience boards have with their property manager.</p>
          <div class="foot">
            <span>7-min read</span>
            <span class="arrow">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m13 6 6 6-6 6"/></svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- START HERE — three most-requested guides -->
  <section class="asks" id="start-here">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="head">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow"><span class="num">No. 02</span><span class="rule-mini"></span>Start here</div>
          <h2>Where most boards <em>start reading.</em></h2>
        </div>
        <p>The three guides HOA and condo boards reach for first &mdash; evaluating management, understanding your reserves, and knowing how the industry actually works. Plain language. No sales pitch.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ask-list">
        <article class="ask">
          <span class="ix">Guide 01</span>
          <h4>How to choose the right management company.</h4>
          <p>What to ask, what to compare, and the questions most boards forget before they sign with anyone. <a href="/solutions/switching-hoa-management/" style="color: var(--innovia-green-deep); font-weight: 600;">Read the guide &rarr;</a></p>
        </article>
        <article class="ask">
          <span class="ix">Guide 02</span>
          <h4>What every board should know about reserve studies.</h4>
          <p>How to read a reserve study, what underfunding looks like, and which questions to bring to your management company. <a href="/board-education/hoa-reserve-study/" style="color: var(--innovia-green-deep); font-weight: 600;">Read the guide &rarr;</a></p>
        </article>
        <article class="ask">
          <span class="ix">Guide 03</span>
          <h4>How HOA management actually works.</h4>
          <p>A clear-eyed breakdown of what a management company does (and doesn&rsquo;t do) &mdash; written for boards, not managers. <a href="/board-education/how-hoa-management-works/" style="color: var(--innovia-green-deep); font-weight: 600;">Read the guide &rarr;</a></p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER — canonical (will be replaced by run_script) -->
  


  
`;
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Resources &amp; Guides for HOA Boards · Innovia Co-op"
  description="A library of cooperatively-authored resources for HOA and condo boards — evaluating management companies, reserve studies, vendor RFPs, governance, and the operating practices Innovia members use."
  ogImage="/assets/og/option-1-type-led.png"
  ctaLabel="Send an Inquiry"
  ctaHref="/find-a-management-company/#request"
>
  <Fragment set:html={html} />
</BaseLayout>
